---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Sáamaka Soul Trust">
	<Header />
	<main>
		<section class="hero">
			<div class="hero-container">
				<div class="hero-content">
					<span class="subtitle">My Story 📚</span>
					<h1>About Me</h1>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="story">
			<div class="story-container">
				<div class="story-text">
					<p class="lead">
						You know the saying "God only gives his strongest soldiers his hardest battles"...?
					</p>
					<p class="highlight">That's me!</p>
					<p>
						During those battles I was the Black Sheep of the family, raising myself and I was a Loner. I really had nobody to turn to! The crazy part about that is that everybody always came to me for everything.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="story-image">
					<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1508214751196-bcfd4ca60f91?w=500&h=600&fit=crop" alt="Portrait" />
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="questions">
			<div class="questions-container">
				<h2>When I Was Fighting My Battles, I Kept Coming Back to 4 Questions:</h2>
				<div class="questions-list">
					<div class="question">
						<span class="number">1</span>
						<p>Why do I have to suffer?</p>
					</div>
					<div class="question">
						<span class="number">2</span>
						<p>Why is it that, despite everything, I still have so much love to give?</p>
					</div>
					<div class="question">
						<span class="number">3</span>
						<p>Why do I long so deeply for love — from family, friends, and a husband — yet have not received it?</p>
					</div>
					<div class="question">
						<span class="number">4</span>
						<p>Why was I always in a struggle just to stay in school?</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="revelation">
			<div class="revelation-container">
				<h2>Now I Know!</h2>
				<div class="quotes">
					<blockquote>
						"I have walked the path myself, and now I guide others along the way."
					</blockquote>
					<blockquote>
						"What I have lived through does not make me a victim – it makes me a guide for those who are still on the journey."
					</blockquote>
				</div>
				<p class="signature">Nankurunaisa ✨</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="mission">
			<div class="mission-container">
				<h2>Missie & Visie</h2>
				<div class="mission-content">
					<div class="mission-block">
						<h3>Missie</h3>
						<p>
							Stichting ondersteunt en begeleidt spirituele, culturele en persoonlijke ontwikkeling - met speciale aandacht voor de Sáamaka gemeenschap - en voor ieder mens die zich spiritueel verbindt met aarde, natuur en erfgoed.
						</p>
						<p>
							Ik geloof dat ware heling ontstaat vanuit verbinding met jezelf, met de natuur, met voorouders en met de community. De stichting is een brug tussen werelden: tussen oud en nieuw, tussen individueel en collectief, tussen innerlijk weten en praktische actie.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="mission-block">
						<h3>Visie</h3>
						<p>
							Een wereld waarin mensen hun donker durven aankijken, zodat ze hun eigen licht leren ontsteken. Mijn merk staat voor waarheid, healing en empowerment - in coaching, kleding en in vastgoed.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	.hero {
		background-color: #000000;
		padding: 4rem;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.hero-container {
		max-width: 1100px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.subtitle {
		font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
		font-size: 1rem;
		color: #c9a227;
		display: block;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	h1 {
		font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
		font-size: 4rem;
		font-weight: 400;
		font-style: italic;
		color: #ffffff;
	}

	.story {
		background-color: #000000;
		padding: 4rem;
	}

	.story-container {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 350px;
		gap: 3rem;
		max-width: 1100px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		align-items: center;
	}

	.story-text .lead {
		font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
		font-size: 1.75rem;
		font-style: italic;
		color: #ffffff;
		line-height: 1.5;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.story-text .highlight {
		font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		font-style: italic;
		color: #c9a227;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.story-text p {
		font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
		font-size: 1rem;
		font-weight: 300;
		line-height: 1.8;
		color: #ffffff;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.story-image img {
		width: 100%;
		height: auto;
		filter: grayscale(100%);
		object-fit: cover;
	}

	.questions {
		background-color: #000000;
		padding: 5rem 4rem;
		border-top: 1px solid #1a1a1a;
	}

	.questions-container {
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.questions h2 {
		font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
		font-size: 2rem;
		font-weight: 400;
		font-style: italic;
		color: #ffffff;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.questions-list {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.question {
		display: flex;
		align-items: flex-start;
		gap: 1.5rem;
	}

	.question .number {
		font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
		font-size: 2rem;
		color: #c9a227;
		line-height: 1;
	}

	.question p {
		font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
		font-size: 1rem;
		font-weight: 300;
		line-height: 1.8;
		color: #ffffff;
	}

	.revelation {
		background-color: #000000;
		padding: 5rem 4rem;
		text-align: center;
		border-top: 1px solid #1a1a1a;
	}

	.revelation-container {
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.revelation h2 {
		font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
		font-size: 3rem;
		font-weight: 400;
		color: #c9a227;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
	}

	.quotes {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 2rem;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.quotes blockquote {
		font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		font-style: italic;
		color: #ffffff;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.signature {
		font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		font-style: italic;
		color: #c9a227;
	}

	.mission {
		background-color: #000000;
		padding: 5rem 4rem;
		border-top: 1px solid #1a1a1a;
	}

	.mission-container {
		max-width: 1100px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.mission h2 {
		font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		font-weight: 400;
		color: #ffffff;
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
	}

	.mission-content {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 3rem;
	}

	.mission-block h3 {
		font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
		font-size: 1.75rem;
		font-weight: 400;
		color: #c9a227;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.mission-block p {
		font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		font-weight: 300;
		line-height: 1.8;
		color: #ffffff;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.hero {
			padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
		}

		h1 {
			font-size: 2.5rem;
		}

		.story {
			padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
		}

		.story-container {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 2rem;
		}

		.story-image {
			order: -1;
			justify-self: center;
		}

		.story-image img {
			max-width: 280px;
		}

		.story-text {
			text-align: center;
		}

		.story-text .lead {
			font-size: 1.5rem;
		}

		.story-text .highlight {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}

		.questions {
			padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
		}

		.questions h2 {
			font-size: 1.5rem;
		}

		.revelation {
			padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
		}

		.revelation h2 {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}

		.quotes blockquote {
			font-size: 1.25rem;
		}

		.mission {
			padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
		}

		.mission-content {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 2rem;
		}
	}
</style>
